🗓 Key #CARecall Dates 🗓 

📬 Aug 16: Ballots sent by mail + early voting starts! 

🗳 Aug 17: Mail ballot drop-off locations open. 
 
📌 Aug 30: Last day to register online by mail (you can still register at your polling place up to/on #ElectionDay).

🗳 Sept 14: #ElectionDay! https://t.co/iJWzoEKoc8
